content: I'm trying to plan out my day and make the most of my time. I have a lot of tasks to complete and I want to make sure I have enough time for everything. Can you help me prioritize my tasks and create a schedule for the day? By the way, I've been trying to establish a consistent wake-up time, which is 7:30 AM on weekdays and 9 AM on weekends, so I'd like to factor that in.
